snippet.title: EcoGnomix | Release Date Announcement (PlayStation, Xbox)
snippet.description:
The future of our gnomes is in your hands! Flex your strategic muscles on the big screen, as EcoGnomix is coming to PlayStation and Xbox on April 25! 

EcoGnomix is a quirky rogue-lite strategy and city-building game. Build a covert business empire, by looting the underground world with a team of gnomes. Combine upgrades strategically to help your gnomes survive an unlimited supply of mystical caves with unique flora and fauna.

Wishlist Now!
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10013265
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/ecognomix/9ntb6kvp4gl0

#indiegames  #ecognomix  #rogulite  #citybuilders  #gaming  

Financially supported by FFF Bayern and the budgetary funds of the Free State of Bavaria.
